NK110(we)001:1: // sgron ma 'bar ba'i don bsdus bzhugs so //
NK110(we)001:2: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK110(we)001:3: sgron ma 'bar ba zhes bya ba rang rig mngon
NK110(we)001:4: sum du gtan la 'bebs par byed pa'i rgyud 'di
NK110(we)001:5: la / bsdus pa'i don gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK110(we)001:6: mtshan gyis gzhung don gsal bar bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:7: gzhung gis rgyud kyi mtshan don gsal bar bstan pa gnyis las /
NK110(we)001:8: mtshan don gong du bstan zin nas /
NK110(we)001:10: gzhung dngos la yan lag gi don gsum ste /
NK110(we)001:11: rgyud zab mo 'byung bar bstan pas rgyud kyi gleng gzhi bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:12: le'u bzhi'i don mdor bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:13: rgyang zhags chu'i sgron me'i tshig don rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK110(we)001:14: dang po gleng gzhi la'ang don gsum ste /
NK110(we)001:15: zab mo don 'di skad bdag gi bstan pa'i dus gcig na /
NK110(we)001:16: gsum gyi rgyud dka' bas thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK110(we)001:17: gleng gzhi ston pa nyid kyis rang la rang ston
NK110(we)001:18: gyi tshul du gsungs pa la /
NK110(we)001:19: sdud pa pos tshig gis ma bcos par bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:20: gleng gzhi gnyis kyi mtshams sbyar ba sgra don sarba a pa la d+ha thim /
NK110(we)001:21: tshig gis chos thams cad la zla bar bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:22: thun mong gi gleng gzhi theg pa thun mong ba
NK110(we)001:23: dang sgo bstun gyi tshul du sdud pa pos tshig
NK110(we)001:24: tu bkod pa'o // lan lag gi don gnyis pa
NK110(we)001:25: le'u bzhi'i don mdor bstan pa la nang don gnyis
NK110(we)001:26: tu bkod pa'o // kyis bstan te / rgyud kyi
NK110(we)001:27: gzhung don nges par rang bzhin rgyud dag rdo rje
NK110(we)001:28: tu bkod pa'o // kyis bstan te / 'chang / 'byung bar byed pa'am che ba bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:29: rgyud kyi tshig don le'u bzhi'i don mdor bstan pa'o //
NK110(we)001:30: yan lag gi don gsum pa /
NK110(we)001:31: rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma'i tshig don rgyas par bshad pa la nang don bzhi ste /
NK110(we)001:33: dri ba mdor bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:34: de nas rgyud dag rdo rje 'chang /
NK110(we)001:36: de nas rdo rje 'chang chen gyis /
NK110(we)001:37: dri ba rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:40: nang don bzhi pa'i tha ma rgyas par bshad pa la dri lan dgus ste /
NK110(we)001:50: dang po rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma'i de bzhin 'khor ba'i /
NK110(we)001:52: ngo bo'i lan bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:53: gnyis pa nges tshig bstan pa la nang tshan gyi don lnga ste /
NK110(we)001:55: nges pa'i tshig ni lta bu /
NK110(we)001:56: 'khor 'das kyi snang ba 'dzin lugs bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:57: snang ba de gnyis chu ni snang ba /
NK110(we)001:58: zhen pa'i dngos po bcad pa'i nges tshig dang /
NK110(we)001:59: de nyid kyis gsal bar sgron ni rang gi snang ba kun /
NK110(we)001:60: byed pa'i nges tshig bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:61: khyab par rig pa phyi'i dbyings /
NK110(we)001:63: dris lan gsum pa dbye ba bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:64: dbye ba rnam pa gsum yin no //
NK110(we)001:66: bzhi pa mtshan nyid bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:67: dris lan lnga pa gnas sa gang na gnas bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:68: dris lan thog ma rang gi lus bskyed pa'i /
NK110(we)001:69: drug pa mig de rang gis shes shing gang dang 'brel bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:70: dris lan bdun pa sgo gang las 'char ba'i sgo ni mig nyid dang /
NK110(we)001:72: dris lan brgyad pa mthun pa'i dpe bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:73: dper na 'dzin byed lcags kyu yis /
NK110(we)001:74: dris lan dgu pa rgyang zhags sgron ma snang bar byed don gyis /
NK110(we)001:75: chu'i tshad tshig gsum gyis bstan pa'o //
NK110(we)001:76: le'u gnyis pa shes rab rang byung gi sgron ma bstan pa 'di la bsdus pa'i don gnyis ste /
NK110(we)001:77: zhu ba mdor bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:79: lan rgyas par bshad pa la dris lan brgyad kyis bstan te /
NK110(we)001:88: dang po shes rab de nas ston pas yang gsungs pa /
NK110(we)001:89: rang byung gi sgron ma'i ngo bo'i lan rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:90: dris lan gnyis po nges tshig bstan pa la nang tshan gyi don lnga ste /
NK110(we)001:91: shes pa'i nges tshig shes pa dngos dang dang po khyod pa'i /
NK110(we)001:93: rab kyi nges tshig rang bzhin dag pa'i chos sku ni /
NK110(we)001:95: shes pa'i rab de gzhan gyis spyod pa'o //
NK110(we)001:96: gzhan ma yin par bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:97: de ltar gzhan ma yin par byas pas 'di don
NK110(we)001:98: rgyu rkyen dang rtsol bsgrub dang bral bar bstan pa
NK110(we)001:100: byas pa las ma yung pa'i shes rab de gnyis
NK110(we)001:101: su med cing kun la khyab pa'i nges tshig bstan
NK110(we)001:102: pa'o // dris lan gsum pa dbye ba dbye na rnam pa lnga yin te /
NK110(we)001:104: dris lan bzhi pa mtshan nyid bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:105: dris lan 'khor ba'i sgo de dbang po lnga /
NK110(we)001:106: lnga pa 'char sgo bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:107: dris lan drug pa shes rab /
NK110(we)001:108: skyed par byed pa'i rtsa bzhi nas /
NK110(we)001:109: kyi gnas sa bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:110: dris lan bdun pa de nyid kyi tshad bstan pa la nang tshan gyi don lnga ste /
NK110(we)001:111: gzhi gnas gzhi gnas rang byung rang byung gi shes rab kyi tshad bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:112: snang ba snang ba cer zin shes rab tshad /
NK110(we)001:113: cer zin gyi shes rab kyi tshad bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:114: dran pa 'gag pa med pa'i shes rab dran pa 'gag med /
NK110(we)001:115: ma brjed pa'i gzungs skyes pa'i tshad bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:116: so sor rtogs pa'i blo so sor rtog pa'i shes rab /
NK110(we)001:117: rim gyi shes pa bskyes pa'i rtags dang tshad bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:118: 'jug byed rnam gsum gyi shes rab kyi tshad bstan pa'o //
NK110(we)001:119: dris lan brgyad pa dpe bstan pa'o //
NK110(we)001:120: da ni le'u gsum pa'i thig le 'jug rnam byed gsum shes rab ni /
NK110(we)001:121: stong pa'i sgron ma 'di la bsdus pa'o dper na spra brlan med pa /
NK110(we)001:123: zhu ba mdor bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:124: de nas rgyu dag rdo rje 'chang lan rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK110(we)001:125: lan rgyas par bshad pa la nang tshan gyi don bcu gnyis ste /
NK110(we)001:126: thig le stong pa'i de nas rdo rje 'chang ba yis /
NK110(we)001:128: gnyis pa nges tshig thig le mi 'gyur drang po la /
NK110(we)001:129: gi lan rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK110(we)001:130: gsum pa dbye ba bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:131: dbye ba nyid ni rnam pa lnga /
NK110(we)001:132: bzhi pa thig le rang gnas dgongs pa gcig yin pas /
NK110(we)001:133: stong pa'i sgron ma'i mtshan nyid dam dgongs pa bstan dang /
NK110(we)001:134: lnga pa sgron ma de nyid sems can kun gyi lus kyi dkyil /
NK110(we)001:135: gnas gang na gnas bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:136: drug pa 'char ba snang ba yis ni 'char byed pa /
NK110(we)001:137: byed pa'i sgo bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:138: bdun pa sgron ma de nyid kyi rang bzhin stong pa nyid las rang log pa'i /
NK110(we)001:139: nam dngos gang yin pa dang /
NK110(we)001:140: brgyad pa bar snang min na stong pa la /
NK110(we)001:141: sgron ma de nyid yul la snang ba bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:142: dgu pa tshad bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:143: thig le spros dang bsdu med par /
NK110(we)001:144: bcu pa sgron ma de nyid 'od la 'dus pa'i thig le ni /
NK110(we)001:145: 'gro ba drug la ji ltar gnas pa bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:146: bcu gcig pa rtog pa'i rang gi 'theb dang 'dzub mo yis /
NK110(we)001:148: de la goms par bya ba'i man ngag bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:149: bcu gnyis pa dper na rma bya'i mdongs dang mtshungs /
NK110(we)001:151: le'u bzhi pa dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma bstan pa'i le'u 'di la don lnga ste /
NK110(we)001:152: zhu ba mdor de nas rgyu dag rdo rje 'chang /
NK110(we)001:154: lan rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK110(we)001:155: rgyud bzung ba'i phan yon bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:162: lan rgyas par bshad pa la don bcu gcig pa ste /
NK110(we)001:164: de nas rdo rje 'chang chen gyis /
NK110(we)001:166: gnyis pa nges rnam pa yul dus snang la /
NK110(we)001:168: gsum pa dbye ba bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:169: dbye ba rnam pa gsum yin te /
NK110(we)001:170: bzhi pa rang bzhin rang bzhin snang ba ma 'gags pas /
NK110(we)001:172: lnga pa dbyings rnam pa dag pa'i sgron ma'i phyi nang med par zang thal bas /
NK110(we)001:173: dgongs pa'am mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:174: drug pa 'khor 'das ru shan phyed nas ni /
NK110(we)001:175: goms par byed pa'i man ngag bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:176: bdun pa de nyid kyi mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:177: mthing ga mi 'gyur snang ba la /
NK110(we)001:178: brgyad pa de nyid kyi gnas pa mig ni 'byung ba skye med pa /
NK110(we)001:180: dgu pa de ltar mig gi rnam shes dag pa la /
NK110(we)001:181: gnas pa'i dbyings rig de sgo gang las 'byung bar bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:182: bcu pa de nyid rang so bstan pa dang /
NK110(we)001:183: 'di ltar gnad gsum man ngag dang /
NK110(we)001:184: bcu gcig pa dper na yi ge na ro bzhin /
NK110(we)001:185: de nyid kyi mthun pa'i dpe bstan pa'o //
NK110(we)001:186: sgron ma 'bar ba'i don bsdus pa /
NK110(we)001:188: dpe yi sgo nas mtshan btags pa /
